<main class="container page-main">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>
    HealthGuide AI is an educational website and does not require an account to read symptom guides.
  </p>
  <h2>Information we may collect</h2>
  <p>
    We may collect basic technical information such as your IP address, browser type, and pages visited.
    This is usually done via analytics tools to understand which pages are most useful and how the site is used.
  </p>
  <p>
    We do not intend to collect identifiable health information. Please avoid entering your full name, address,
    or personal identifiers into any forms or search boxes.
  </p>
  <h2>Cookies and advertising</h2>
  <p>
    This site may use cookies or similar technologies to support analytics and advertising (for example,
    if we add Google AdSense). Third-party providers may use their own cookies to show relevant ads.
  </p>
  <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
  <p>
    Some links to products may be affiliate links. If you click on an affiliate link and make a purchase,
    we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you.
  </p>
  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <p>
    You can adjust your browser settings to control cookies. If you do not agree with this policy, please
    do not use this website.
  </p>

  <div class="disclaimer-box">
    HealthGuide AI is for educational purposes only and does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.
  </div>
</main>

